     "xbrltype": "textBlockItemType",
     "nsuri": "http://fasb.org/us-gaap/2025",', "[WEB ARAMASI KAYNAĞI]: Yerel veri tabanında bulunamayan bilgi için internet ve finansal API'ler üzerinden şu güncel veriler elde edilmiştir:
Tesla does have preferred stock, with a par value of $0.001. However, it is important to note that there are 100 shares authorized, but no shares are issued and outstanding. 

For more details, you can refer to the [Tesla Investor Relations document](https://ir.tesla.com/_flysystem/s3/sec/000119312520236699/d931870d424b5.html)."]
